Parliament, Wednesday, 10 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Service will tomorrow, 11 October 2018, receive briefings from the Public Protector South Africa, the South African Human Rights Commission and the Information Regulator on its annual reports. Details of the meeting are as follows: 
	Date: Thursday, 11 October 2018
	Time: 09:00
	Venue: Committee Room Old Assembly Chamber, Ground Floor, Old Assembly Building. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON JUSTICE AND CORRECTIONAL SERVICES, MS MADIPOANE, REFILOE MOREMADI MOTHAPO For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)Tel: 021 403 8437Cell: 081 703 9542E-mail: razzakani@parliament.gov.za Bills can only be introduced in Parliament by Ministers, Deputy Ministers, parliamentary committees and individual MPs.Read more